 se on the page in Arabic (Uthmani)\, English (Sahih International)\, Swedi
 sh (Bernström)\, with Hijri date. Lite variant: no tafsir. For tafsir\, s
 ubscribe to the full version. Starts 2026-08-31. Runs sequentially through
  all 604 mushaf pages.
