 َ\n\nEN: They will say\, "Our Lord\, our wretchedness overcame us\, and w
 e were a people astray.\nSV: De skall svara: "Herre! Vårt onda öde beseg
 rade oss och vi gick vilse.\n\n-- 23:107 --\n\nرَبَّنَآ أَخْ
