 بْدٍ مُّنِيبٍ\n\nEN: Then\, do they not look at what is before
  them and what is behind them of the heaven and earth? If We should will\,
  We could cause the earth to swallow them or [could] let fall upon them fr
 agments from the sky. Indeed in that is a sign for every servant turning b
 ack [to Allāh].\nSV: Ser de inte att de [var de än står] på alla sidor
  omges av [Vår] himmel och [Vår] jord? Om Vi ville\, kunde Vi låta jord
