 لِحًا ۖ إِنِّى بِمَا تَعْمَلُونَ بَصِير
 ٌ\n\nEN: [Commanding him]\, "Make full coats of mail and calculate [preci
 sely] the links\, and work [all of you] righteousness. Indeed I\, of what 
 you do\, am Seeing."\nSV: [och befallde honom] att tillverka rymliga brynj
