 رُوهَا فَدَمْدَمَ عَلَيْهِمْ رَبُّهُم ب
 ِذَنۢبِهِمْ فَسَوَّىٰهَا\n\nEN: But they denied him
  and hamstrung¹ her. So their Lord brought down upon them destruction for
